    "In the visual representation, these descriptions from the forms are compiled and graphically represented in three-dimensional formats.",
    "In the formalized rules, specifications are outlined detailing how NHP interact within their environment (Bourlakis 2009; Sébastien et al. 2009; Patrick 2009; Jaung 2022; Meta 2021).",
